### Login para obtener token JWT
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@fincorral.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Test endpoint público (sin token)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/test/public

### Test endpoint protegido (con token)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/test/protected
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear Cliente (requiere token)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/clientes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan.perez@email.com",
  "telefono": "555-1234"
}

### Obtener todos los clientes (requiere token)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear Préstamo Ordinario (requiere token)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/prestamos/ordinario
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "clienteId": 1,
  "monto": 2000,
  "fechaPrimerPago": "2024-01-15T00:00:00"
}